description:
Within Academy City, the Level 5s are the most powerful psychics in the city. The following are the currently known Level 5s; ranked not by strength but by how useful they are to http://anidb.net/ch2731 [Aleister]`s plans.
1.) http://anidb.net/ch10527 [Accelerator]
2.) http://anidb.net/ch98257 [Kakine Teitoku]
3.) http://anidb.net/ch2469 [Misaka Mikoto]
4.) http://anidb.net/ch56199 [Mugino Shizuri]
5.) http://anidb.net/ch54960 [Shokuhou Misaki]
6.) Unknown. A possible impersonator claiming to be Aihana Etsu has appeared.
7.) http://anidb.net/ch107656 [Sogiita Gunha]
name: Level 5
